<plot>Copywriter Conrad Bloom is a "nice guy" in New York City whose life is filled with interesting women: His mother, his sister, an ex-girlfriend, his lady boss and a female co-worker. This situation comedy explores his relationships with those women as well as his life as a young male reaching the crossroads of adulthood in the nineties.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?114203</url></doc>
